### Claude Code UI Frontend Testing
### Frontend Dev Server (Port 3009) - Tests Vite Proxy

@frontendUrl = http://localhost:3009
@token = your-auth-token-here

### Frontend - Health Check (proxied to backend)
GET {{frontendUrl}}/api/health
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Frontend - Auth Status (proxied to backend)
GET {{frontendUrl}}/api/auth/status
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Frontend - Login (proxied to backend)
POST {{frontendUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "admin"
}

###

### Frontend - Get User Info (proxied to backend, requires auth)
GET {{frontendUrl}}/api/auth/user
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Frontend - Get Server Config (proxied to backend, requires auth)
GET {{frontendUrl}}/api/config
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Frontend - Get Projects (proxied to backend, requires auth)
GET {{frontendUrl}}/api/projects
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Frontend - MCP CLI List (proxied to backend, requires auth)
GET {{frontendUrl}}/api/mcp/cli/list
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Frontend - Static Assets Test
GET {{frontendUrl}}/
Accept: text/html

###

### Frontend - Vite Dev Server Info
GET {{frontendUrl}}/vite-dev-server-info
Accept: application/json

